<sect1>
 <title>Feedback</title>

 <para>
  Several feedback channels are available:
 </para>

 <variablelist>
  <varlistentry os="osuse">
   <term>Bugs and Enhancement Requests</term>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     To report bugs for a product component, or to submit enhancement
     requests, please use <ulink url="https://bugzilla.novell.com/"/>. For
     documentation bugs, submit a bug against the component
     <guimenu>Documentation</guimenu> for the respective product.
    </para>
    <para>
     If you are new to Bugzilla, you might find the following articles
     helpful:
    </para>
    <itemizedlist>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       <ulink url="http://ru.opensuse.org/openSUSE:Сообщить_об_ошибке"/>
      </para>
     </listitem>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       <ulink url="http://ru.opensuse.org/openSUSE:Bug_reporting_FAQ"/>
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
   </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry os="sles;sled;slepos">
   <term>Bugs and Enhancement Requests</term>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     For services and support options available for your product, refer to
     <ulink url="http://www.novell.com/services/"></ulink>.
    </para>
    <para>
     To report bugs for a product component, please use
     <ulink
    url="http://support.novell.com/additional/bugreport.html"/>.
    </para>
    <para>
     Submit enhancement requests at
     <ulink
      url="https://secure-www.novell.com/rms/rmsTool?action=ReqActions.viewAddPage&amp;return=www"
     />.
    </para>
   </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
  <varlistentry>
   <term>User Comments</term>
   <listitem>
    <para>
     We want to hear your comments and suggestions about this manual and the
     other documentation included with this product. Use the User Comments
     feature at the bottom of each page in the online documentation or go to
     <ulink
      url="http://www.novell.com/documentation/feedback.html"/>
     and enter your comments there.
    </para>
   </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
 </variablelist>
</sect1>
